{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"firstLine","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"VerticalAlignment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This alignment is analogous to the default behavior of SwiftUI’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"Label","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", where","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the icon is vertically centered with the first line of the label text. Unlike","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"Label","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", this alignment can be used with any view, any spacing, and any number","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of subviews.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The alignment uses SwiftUI’s text baseline alignment guides to calculate the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"center of the first line. It works by finding the difference between the first","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and last text baselines, then computing the midpoint of the remaining height.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Usage","anchor":"Usage","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use ","type":"text"},{"code":".firstLine","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" as the alignment parameter for ","type":"text"},{"code":"HStack","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["HStack(alignment: .firstLine, spacing: 12) {","  Image(systemName: \"star.fill\")","    .foregroundStyle(.yellow)","  VStack(alignment: .leading) {","    Text(\"First Line\")","      .font(.headline)","    Text(\"Second Line\")","    Text(\"Third Line\")","  }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The star icon will be vertically centered with “First Line”, regardless of how"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"many additional lines of text appear below."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Common Use Cases","anchor":"Common-Use-Cases","type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Timeline entries"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Align node indicators with the first line of event descriptions"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"List items"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Align icons or checkboxes with the first line of multiline labels"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Form fields"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Align validation icons with the first line of error messages"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Comments\/Reviews"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Align avatars with the first line of comment text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"text":"How It Works","anchor":"How-It-Works","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The alignment calculates:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The height after the first line: "},{"code":"lastTextBaseline - firstTextBaseline","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The height of the first line: "},{"code":"totalHeight - heightAfterFirstLine","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The center point: "},{"code":"heightOfFirstLine \/ 2","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This positions the alignment guide at the vertical center of the first line of text."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment\/firstLine","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"firstLine","fragments":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"firstLine","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"VerticalAlignment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV"}],"extendedModule":"SwiftUICore","roleHeading":"Type Property","externalID":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV8IronCoreE9firstLineACvpZ","modules":[{"relatedModules":["SwiftUICore"],"name":"IronCore"}],"symbolKind":"property"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Aligns content to the center of the first line of text."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore\/verticalalignment\/firstline"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore","doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore","doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore/SwiftUICore/VerticalAlignment/firstLine":{"type":"topic","title":"firstLine","identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment\/firstLine","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Aligns content to the center of the first line of text.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"firstLine","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"VerticalAlignment","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore\/verticalalignment\/firstline","kind":"symbol"},"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore":{"type":"topic","title":"IronCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Foundation module providing theming, tokens, and accessibility utilities.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/ironcore","kind":"symbol"},"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore/SwiftUICore":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore","role":"collection","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore","title":"SwiftUICore"},"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore/SwiftUICore/VerticalAlignment":{"url":"\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore\/verticalalignment","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment","abstract":[{"text":"Provides first-line text alignment for use in HStack layouts.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"extension"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV","kind":"identifier","text":"VerticalAlignment"}],"title":"VerticalAlignment","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"VerticalAlignment","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"}}}